---

<section class="pres-review">
  <div class="pres-review__container">
    <div class="pres-review__intro">
      <p class="pres-review__eyebrow">Diligence before you fund</p>
      <h2 class="pres-review__heading">Review the documents <em>before you invest.</em></h2>
      <p class="pres-review__body">
        You do not need to create an account to read the core offering documents. Start with the
        SEC-filed Offering Circular, review the bond agreement, or book a 10-minute call and a real
        person will walk through them with you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ul class="pres-review__list" aria-label="Offering documents">
      <li class="pres-review__item">
        <a
          class="pres-review__link"
          href="#"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          data-track-cta="offering_circular"
          data-track-location="review_block"
        >
          <span class="pres-review__link-title">Offering Circular</span>
          <span class="pres-review__link-desc">
            The SEC-filed offering details: risk factors, financials, use of proceeds, and bond
            terms.
          </span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="pres-review__item">
        <a
          class="pres-review__link"
          href="#"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          data-track-cta="sample_bond_agreement"
          data-track-location="review_block"
        >
          <span class="pres-review__link-title">Sample Bond Agreement</span>
          <span class="pres-review__link-desc">
            The contract terms investors sign inside InvestorDesk before funding.
          </span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="pres-review__item">
        <a
          class="pres-review__link pres-review__link--accent"
          href="/offer/book-call"
          data-track-cta="book_call"
          data-track-location="review_block"
        >
          <span class="pres-review__link-title">Book a 10-minute call</span>
          <span class="pres-review__link-desc">
            Ask the team to walk through the documents with you before you create an account.
          </span>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="pres-review__footnote">
      InvestorDesk is where you create your account, sign, and fund. This page and the documents
      above are how you review the offering first.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pres-review {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-review__container {
    max-width: 1136px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .pres-review__intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .pres-review__eyebrow {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 130%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pres-review__heading {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 120%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-review__heading em {
    color: var(--green-dark);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .pres-review__body {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #555555;
    line-height: 150%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-review__heading + .pres-review__body {
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .pres-review__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .pres-review__item {
    display: flex;
  }

  .pres-review__link {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green-brand);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    flex: 1;
    transition:
      border-color 0.2s ease,
      box-shadow 0.2s ease,
      transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pres-review__link:hover {
    border-left-color: var(--green-dark);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .pres-review__link--accent {
    background: var(--green-tint);
    border-left-color: var(--green-dark);
  }

  .pres-review__link-title {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 130%;
  }

  .pres-review__link-desc {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 150%;
  }

  .pres-review__footnote {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 160%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .pres-review__container {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      gap: 36px;
    }

    .pres-review__intro {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .pres-review__heading {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .pres-review__list {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pres-review__container {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }

    .pres-review__heading {
      font-size: 2.75rem;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1136px) {
    .pres-review__heading {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
